WEBVTT

00:01.012 --> 00:05.381
Sync and corrections by n17t01
www.addic7ed.com

00:06.466 --> 00:08.867
<i>Air and naval
forces</i> <i>of the United States</i>

00:08.900 --> 00:11.698
<i>launched a series of strikes</i>
<i>against terrorist facilities...</i>

00:11.732 --> 00:13.697
<i>Pan Am Flight 103 crashed</i>
<i>into the the town of Lockerbie.</i>

00:13.731 --> 00:15.161
<i>He has sanctioned</i>
<i>acts of terror</i>

00:15.195 --> 00:17.829
<i>in Africa, Europe,</i>
<i>the Middle East.</i>

00:17.863 --> 00:20.465
<i>This will not stand,</i>
<i>this</i> <i>aggression against, uh, Kuwait.</i>

00:20.500 --> 00:22.201
<i>REAGAN:</i> <i>This relentless
pursuit</i> <i>of terror.</i>

00:22.235 --> 00:23.837
PRESIDENT GEORGE W.
<i>We will make no distinction...</i>

00:23.871 --> 00:25.343
<i>The</i> USS Cole <i>was attacked</i>

00:25.377 --> 00:26.542
<i>while refueling in</i>
<i>the port of Aden.</i>

00:26.576 --> 00:28.509
This was an act of terrorism.

00:28.543 --> 00:31.008
It was a despicable
and cowardly act.

00:31.042 --> 00:33.343
<i>The next song</i>
<i>we're going to play for you</i>

00:33.377 --> 00:34.511
is one of the good old
favorites.

00:34.545 --> 00:36.917
Until something stops him.

00:36.952 --> 00:39.986
<i>I'm just making sure</i>
<i>we don't get hit again.</i>

00:40.020 --> 00:43.554
<i>That plane crashed</i>
<i>into the World Trade Center.</i>

00:44.922 --> 00:47.188
<i>Thousands of people running.</i>

00:47.222 --> 00:50.893
We must and we will remain
vigilant at home and abroad.

00:57.537 --> 01:00.005
<i>What the fuck are you doing?</i>

01:00.039 --> 01:02.007
God!

01:02.041 --> 01:04.010
<i>Fuck! I missed</i>
<i>something once before.</i>

01:04.044 --> 01:06.812
<i>I won't...</i>
<i>I</i> can't <i>let that happen again.</i>

01:08.080 --> 01:10.214
<i>It was ten years ago.</i>

01:10.248 --> 01:11.915
<i>Everyone missed something</i>
<i>that day.</i>

01:11.949 --> 01:13.918
<i>Everyone's not me.</i>

